results.name: This sequence and A324143 are a pair of complementary sequences studied by Bode, Harborth, and Kimberling (2007).
comment: This pair of sequences is the first example in the Bode, Harborth, and Kimberling (2007) paper. See A022424 for a list of a large number of other pairs of complementary sequences based on the same paper.
link: Lars Blomberg, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
J-P. Bode, H. Harborth, C. Kimberling, Complementary Fibonacci sequences, Fibonacci Quarterly 45 (2007), 254-264.
